description:
In this Everything Iconic POP Dive, Danny welcomes Kardashian expert Ryan Bailey (host of the Realizing Stuff podcast) to talk about the Keeping Up With The Kardashians pilot, the legacy and future of the show, how it has influences reality TV, favorite moments, and more.


*For bonus episodes & to support the podcast, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
